These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
House: farmhouse, wooden, futuristic, modern
Color: white, grey, mauve, amber
1. House:farmhouse is on the right of Color:mauve##1
2. Color:amber is on the far left##1
3. Color:mauve is between Color:grey and House:wooden##2
4. House:modern is on the far left##1
5. House:futuristic is between House:wooden and House:farmhouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| House   | modern         | wooden   | futuristic | farmhouse       |
| Color      | amber | white | mauve   | grey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Job: architect, fisherman, entrepreneur, pilot
Beverage: milk, water, lemonade, fanta
1. Beverage:fanta is between Job:entrepreneur and Beverage:water##2
2. Job:pilot is on the far right##1
3. Beverage:lemonade is on the right of Beverage:milk##1
4. Job:architect is on the left of Beverage:milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Job         | fisherman | architect | entrepreneur | pilot |
| Beverage   | water    | fanta   | milk | lemonade       |

