Cigar: dunhill, prince, bolivar, bluemaster
1. Cigar:bolivar is on the right of Pet:turtle##1
2. Cigar:bolivar is between Cigar:prince and Pet:guinea-pig##2
3. Cigar:prince is on the far left##1
4. Cigar:bluemaster is on the left of Pet:rat##1
5. Pet:guinea-pig == Cigar:bluemaster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Pet          | turtle    | ferret | guinea-pig   | rat  |
| Cigar   | prince | bolivar   | bluemaster | dunhill |

